---
title: Honey-Soy Chicken & Flat Noodles with Roasted Peanuts
description: Forget the sticky, greasy take-away noodle dishes you’ve tried in the past, and welcome these noodles into your life! It’s best enjoyed with chopsticks as the noodles are so morish and saucy you'll want to savour every mouthful.
